Package: MultipleTestingBoosting
Title: High-Dimensional Model Selection Using MTB
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Charisios", "Grivas", email = "charisios.grivas@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The package implements the Multiple Testing Boosting procedure for model selection in high-dimensional
    settings such as linear and probit/logit models. The methods have been developed by G. Kapetanios, V. Sarafidis,
    A. Ventouri (2025) and C. Grivas, G. Kapetanios, Z. Psaradakis, V. Sarafidis, A. Ventouri and M. Vavra (2026) respectively.
